  Numeric Columns:

  - âœ… Format: Positive integers or decimals
  - âœ… Examples: 150, 0, 1.5, 2000.0

  Missing Data:

  - âœ… Allowed: Empty cells, null, "", 0
  - âŒ Avoid: N/A, #VALUE!, -1

  ---
  ğŸ¯ Best Practices

  1. Data Quality:

  âœ… GOOD:
  date,location,new_cases,new_deaths
  2024-01-01,New York,150,5
  2024-01-02,New York,142,3

  âŒ BAD:
  date,location,new_cases,new_deaths
  Jan 1,NY,150,five
  1/2/24,,142,

  2. Consistent Locations:

  âœ… GOOD: Use consistent naming
  New York,New York,New York

  âŒ BAD: Inconsistent naming
  New York,NY,New York State

  3. Date Consistency:

  âœ… GOOD: Same format throughout
  2024-01-01,2024-01-02,2024-01-03

  âŒ BAD: Mixed formats
  2024-01-01,1/2/2024,Jan 3 2024

